{"tid":2488323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要抱著香港必須死的陰暗想法去證明自己的移民決定是「對」","createTime":"2021-04-14T07:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T07:20:16.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b663406fb20ae4ca8e145721eb806f3bb1383c17","tid":2488323,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lewis.dadazim/posts/10226157016248798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flewis.dadazim%2Fposts%2F10226157016248798&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=020b413d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lewis.dadazim/posts/10226157016248798</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Lewis Loud<br />\n<br />\n對移民問題，始終的底線是，你走了，不要抱著自己一定做得比別人對的自榮，也不要抱著香港必須死的陰暗想法去證明自己的移民決定是「對」。<br />\n<br />\n你是香港人，不應渴望見到香港死、香港無空間、香港再沒事可為。<br />\n<br />\n外國人中國人這樣想我不怪他們，但香港人自己這樣想，just showing the world who you really are"},{"pid":"4961734e9737b4335f1fa4d3872e8e671be872b3","tid":2488323,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"香港死就證明<br />\n1. 中共無力托巿<br />\n2. 中共無法用香港做白手套，西方完全封鎖中國<br />\n<br />\n所以香港死可以話係支爆嘅先兆"},{"pid":"c67c0b4826278a7406b33e4ea59cd4fa842fc71c","tid":2488323,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"咁佢又有咩高見？<br />\n香港唔死又點樣光復香港？<br />\n無人會幫香港人打，但you no gun 點打共產黨？"},{"pid":"82e8888a06bf9137ab74f04e779d9a880bc5abbf","tid":2488323,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"香港已經輸咗"},{"pid":"4b28647e034e4223b3a3c6a7166385b63a084ef7","tid":2488323,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"香港唔死中共又點會傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be348999f7db735991a0d390dac7d8cd6a835db1","tid":2488323,"uid":394759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim